[TooltipLink dataFor:"rovnostmatic"][HeaderWithInfo tag:"h4"]1. Rovnosť matíc[/HeaderWithInfo][/TooltipLink]

[ReactTooltip id:"rovnostmatic" className:"tooltipWhiteBig"]
Nech [Equation]\mathbf{A}[/Equation] a [Equation]\mathbf{B}[/Equation] sú matice rovnakého typu [Equation]m\times n[/Equation],[br /]
kde [Equation]m,n \in N[/Equation]. Matice [Equation]\mathbf{A}[/Equation] a [Equation]\mathbf{B}[/Equation] sa rovnajú, ak platí

[Equation display:true]
a_{ij}= b_{ij},
[/Equation]

pre každé [Equation]i=1,\ldots,m[/Equation] a [Equation]j=1,\ldots,n[/Equation].
[/ReactTooltip]

[link text:"Príklad 1" url:"https://matematika.fberg.tuke.sk/zosit1/2/pr1.pdf" /]

[TooltipLink dataFor:"sucetrozdielmatic"][HeaderWithInfo tag:"h4"]2. Súčet matíc (Rozdiel matíc)[/HeaderWithInfo][/TooltipLink]

[ReactTooltip id:"sucetrozdielmatic" className:"tooltipWhiteBig"]

Nech [Equation]\mathbf{A}=(a_{ij})_{m\times{}n}[/Equation] a [Equation]\mathbf{B}=(b_{ij})_{m\times{}n}[/Equation] sú matice rovnakého typu [Equation]m \times n[/Equation],[br /]
kde [Equation]m,n \in N[/Equation]. Súčet matíc [Equation]\mathbf{A}[/Equation] a [Equation]\mathbf{B}[/Equation] je matica

[Equation display:true]
\mathbf{C}=\mathbf{A}+\mathbf{B}=(c_{ij})_{m\times{}n}
[/Equation]

[Equation display:true]
\mathbf{D}=\mathbf{A}-\mathbf{B}=(d_{ij})_{m\times{}n}
[/Equation]

taká, že pre každé [Equation]i=1,\ldots,m[/Equation] a [Equation]j=1,\ldots,n[/Equation], platí

[Equation display:true]
c_{ij}=a_{ij}+b_{ij} (d_{ij}=a_{ij}- b_{ij}).
[/Equation]

[/ReactTooltip]

[link text:"Príklad 2" url:"https://matematika.fberg.tuke.sk/zosit1/2/pr2.pdf" /]

[TooltipLink dataFor:"sucinmatic"][HeaderWithInfo tag:"h4"]3. Súčin matíc[/HeaderWithInfo][/TooltipLink]

[ReactTooltip id:"sucinmatic" className:"tooltipWhiteBig"]
Nech sú dané matice [Equation]\mathbf{A}=\left(a_{ij}\right)_{m \times n}[/Equation] a
[Equation]\mathbf{B}=\left(b_{ij}\right)_{n \times p}[/Equation].[br /]
Súčinom matíc [Equation]\mathbf{A}[/Equation] a [Equation]\mathbf{B}[/Equation] rozumieme maticu [Equation]\mathbf{C}=\mathbf{A}\cdot\mathbf{B}=\left(c_{ij}\right)_{m \times p}[/Equation], kde

[Equation display:true]
c_{ij}= \sum_{k=1}^n a_{ik} \cdot b_{kj} = a_{i1} \cdot b_{1j}+a_{i2} \cdot b_{2j}+\cdots+a_{in} \cdot b_{nj},
[/Equation]

pre každé [Equation]i=1,\ldots, m[/Equation] a [Equation]j=1,\ldots, n[/Equation], kde [Equation]m,n,p \in \Nu[/Equation].

#### Násobenie matice konštantou

[Equation]k[/Equation]-násobkom matice [Equation]\mathbf{A}=(a_{ij})_{m\times{}n}[/Equation] nazývame maticu [Equation]\mathbf{F}=(f_{ij})_{m\times{}n}[/Equation],[br /]
pričom pre všetky [Equation]{i=1,\ldots,m}[/Equation] a [Equation]{j=1,\ldots,n}[/Equation], kde [Equation]m,n \in N[/Equation], platí

[Equation display:true]
f_{ij}=k\cdot a_{ij}.
[/Equation]

Zapisujeme [Equation]\mathbf{F}=k\cdot\mathbf{A}[/Equation].
[/ReactTooltip]

